
NAME

  **caterpillar** - play a game of Caterpillar

SYNOPSIS

    caterpillar 

DESCRIPTION

    Run this command to play a game of Caterpillar. Any arguments supplied will be ignored.
    The game will take control of the screen, and play until the user presses q.

OPTIONS
    
    -h, --help:  output usage information and exit

SEE ALSO

    [pixelassault](/bin/man/pixelassault)